name: Date picker
description:
Hi Figma community!

I'm really happy to share the Date Picker with Figma community. I've prepared very flexible and easily customizable components that you can use on your own projects for Free.


Implemented updates

  1. More use cases
  2. Date range presets (Last 30, 60, 90 days, etc).
  3. Double-view calendar.
  4. Dark mode.
